textfsm_template:
Value PEER_ID (\S+)
Value TCP_CONNECTION (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value MSGS_SENT (\d+)
Value MSGS_RCVD (\d+)
Value UPTIME (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)

Start
  ^Peer LDP Identifier:\s+${PEER_ID}
  ^\s*TCP Connection:\s+${TCP_CONNECTION}
  ^\s*State:\s+${STATE};\s+Msgs sent/rcvd:\s+${MSGS_SENT}/${MSGS_RCVD};\s+Downstream-Up time:\s+${UPTIME}
  ^\s*LDP Discovery Sources:
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}:\s+xmit/recv -> Record
